  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>LET's DRIFT!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/c9697577fcbec81def599bd687a4f381.avif?t=1774212626\" width=434 height=198 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pick your favorite car, tune it to perfection, and compete against players worldwide.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/f1455733fc28bf78d55b584b40472044.poster.avif?t=1774212626\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/f1455733fc28bf78d55b584b40472044.webm?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/f1455733fc28bf78d55b584b40472044.mp4?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wheel Support.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/02507ad8e2b6d5689ea70f081509da68.poster.avif?t=1774212626\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/02507ad8e2b6d5689ea70f081509da68.webm?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/02507ad8e2b6d5689ea70f081509da68.mp4?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> Customize your ride your way - upgrade the engine, change rims and colors, and design your own liveries. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/04972c8d58e564fdf10517100bdd9799.poster.avif?t=1774212626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/04972c8d58e564fdf10517100bdd9799.webm?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/04972c8d58e564fdf10517100bdd9799.mp4?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master challenging drift tracks, climb the leaderboards, and become the ultimate DRIFT KING. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/aa5c9e20c391dda5d43769c2d093035e.poster.avif?t=1774212626\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/aa5c9e20c391dda5d43769c2d093035e.webm?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469690/extras/aa5c9e20c391dda5d43769c2d093035e.mp4?t=1774212626\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
